Description:
The BEST in TIMBERTOP
"You want the best in Timbertop, well now you've got it."
This modern and contemporary home will tick all the boxes and more. Located in the hub of Timbertop, Officer's premier estate, the property is close to public transport and will be within walking distance to the proposed Timbertop Primary School.
Only 18-months-old, this Porter Davis family home has been made with love and care and is immaculately presented.
From the well manicured gardens to the high ceilings you will not need to look further.
Showcasing:
- Oversized master bedroom with large walk-in robes with shelves PLUS private study nook & split system;
- Ensuite with his and hers vanities and bath;
- Enclosed theatre room room;
- Open plan kitchen living with caesarstone bench tops and ample cupboard space as well as walk-in pantry;
- Stainless steel appliances including dishwasher;
- Split system to living room;
- Remaining 3 bedrooms with built-in robes; 2 bedrooms with split systems;
- 3rd living area/kids retreat;
- Pergola;
- Double lock up garage.
Like I said, you can't beat Barnsley.

RUSH ON IN TO RUSH LILY - OWNERS WANT OFFERS
"Affordable yet appealing."
Dotted in the popular Arena estate, the property is an ideal first home or a profitable rental for any astute investor. Walking distance from the Arena shopping centre, only a few hundred metres from public transport and extremely close to train station, schools and football grounds make the position of this property one of the best in the estate.
The house itself is the definition of a "walk-in and do nothing". All the hard work has been done. Recently painted, re-grouted and landscaped, the house looks almost brand new.
Featuring:
- Four large bedrooms;
- Master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Theatre room;
- High ceilings;
- Massive kitchen with 900 mm stainless steel appliances;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage with internal access;
- Security systems and other safety features;
- Low-maintenance yard, synthetic turf and concreted court yard means there is no mowing required.

HERE IT IS
"Situated in Arena's peaceful south-side you'll find a townhouse that feels anything but."
Almost like yin and yang, on the north side of the property you're greeted with modern living with all the benefits of the Arena estate, one of Officer's premier areas. On the south side you have a tranquil setting adjacent to wetlands and native trees where you'll be consumed by nature and a soft setting sun.
All the while you are walking distance to the Cardinia Train Station, Arena shopping centre and some of the best local schools.
The townhouse itself is immaculate. Featuring:
- 3 bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- A well appointed kitchen with large bench tops;
- A dining area plus adjacent living room;
- Separate lounge room;
- Private decked entertaining area;
- Double car garage with internal access.
Relax, unwind, your home is here.
